While reviewing `lib/ProductOpener/Ingredients.pm`, I noticed an unused variable `$singular` lingering in two of the regexp initialization functions (`init_allergens_regexps` and `init_labels_regexps`).

In both places, the pattern looks exactly like this:

```perl
my $singular = $suffix;     # <-- assigned here
$suffix =~ s/s$//;
$allergens_regexps{$allergens_lc} .= '|' . $suffix . '|' . $suffix . 's';
